A full-stack AI-powered tax filing platform for Indian taxpayers with:

| Layer | Technology | Status |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| **Backend** | FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + SQLite | ✅ Running |
| **Frontend** | Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS SPA | ✅ Running |
| **Tax Engine** | FY 2025-26 slabs (Old + New regime) | ✅ Verified |
| **Auth** | JWT + bcrypt | ✅ Working |

