## How to Run

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Backend
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m uvicorn main:app --port 8000

# Terminal 2 — Frontend
cd frontend
python -m http.server 3000
```

Open http://localhost:3000
